<p><em>Once</em> magazine was a project for my magazine design class at Emerson Collegeâ€™s Publishing MA program. The premise was of a magazine covering various folk tale, fairy tale, and fantasy topics.</p>

<h3 id="description">Description</h3>

<p><img src="../../img/oncemagazine/1a-cover.jpg" alt="Front cover of magazine" />
<img src="../../img/oncemagazine/1b-back-cover.jpg" alt="Back cover of magazine" />
<em>For the back cover, I took a public domain image of a German postage stamp and edited it in Photoshop</em></p>

<p><img src="../../img/oncemagazine/2a-toc-spread.jpg" alt="The table of contents, laid out as a map" />
<em>To add to the whimsical nature of the project, I decided to make the table of contents into a map. I illustrated some images and combined them in Photoshop along with the appropriate text</em></p>

